quran[11{c,v,t}:
3,122,"yaad karo jab tum mein se do giroh buzdali daal khanay par amaada hogaye thay, halaank Allah un ki madad par mojood tha aur mominoun ko Allah hi par bharosa rakhna chahiye"
3,123,"aakhir is se pehlay jung badar mein Allah tumhari madad kar chuka tha halaank is waqt tum bohat kamzor thay lehaza tum ko chahiye ke Allah ki na shukar y se bachcho, umeed hai ke ab tum shukar guzaar bano ge"
3,124,"yaad karo jab tum mominoun se keh rahay thay,"" kya tumahray liye yeh baat kaafi nahi ke Allah teen hazaar farishtay utaar kar tumhari madad kere? """
3,125,"be shak, agar tum sabr karo aur khuda se drtay hue kaam karo to jis aan dushman tumahray oopar charh kar ayen ge usi aan tumhara rab ( teen hazaar nahi ) paanch hazaar sahib nishaan firshton se tumhari madad kere ga"
3,126,yeh baat Allah ne tumhe is liye bta di hai ke tum khush ho jao aur tumahray dil mutmaen ho jayen fatah o nusrat jo kuch bhi hai Allah ki taraf se hai jo barri qowat wala aur Dana o Beena hai
3,127,"( aur yeh madad woh tumhe is liye day ga ) taakay kufar ki raah chalne walon ka aik baazu kaat day, ya un ko aisi zaleel shikast day ke woh naa-muraadi ke sath paspaa ho jayen"
3,128,"(ae Peghamber Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam) faisla ke ikhtiyarat mein tumhara koi hissa nahi, Allah ko ikhtiyar hai chahay inhen maaf kere, chahay saza day kyunkay woh zalim hain"
3,129,"zameen aur asmano mein jo kuch hai is ka maalik Allah hai, jis ko chahay bakhash day aur jis ko chahay azaab day, o hay maaf karne wala aur Raheem hai"
3,130,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, yeh barhta aur charhata sood khana chore do aur Allah se daro, umeed hai ke Falah pao ge"
3,131,uss aag se bachcho jo kafiroon ke liye muhayya ki gayi hai
3,132,"aur Allah aur rasool ka hukum maan lau, tawaqqa hai ke tum par reham kya jaye ga"
